  <h2>About me</h2>
  
  <p>Hi! I'm Alfie, an aspiring software developer who has enjoyed programming since I was young. My interest in software began through video games - I wanted to understand how they were made, so I started creating my own. One of my favourite projects is 
  <a href="#asteroid-shooter"Asteroid Shooter></a> 
